{"type":"message","id":"5cf4617c","parentId":"12c127df","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:36:21.433Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5ebb7ecaff624ccf9113d46c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"⚠️ 股价预警\n\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 | 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| 601857 | 中国石油 | ¥11.95 | -7.51% | ¥-0.97 | 2026-03-10 14:28:49 |\n| 601808 | 中海油服 | ¥17.90 | -6.82% | ¥-1.31 | 2026-03-10 14:28:49 |\n| 600256 | 广汇能源 | ¥6.71 | -5.36% | ¥-0.38 | 2026-03-10 14:28:49 |\n| 600583 | 海油工程 | ¥7.20 | -4.13% | ¥-0.31 | 2026-03-10 14:28:49 |\n| 000852 | 石化机械 | ¥8.08 | -3.92% | ¥-0.33 | 2026-03-10 14:28:49 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > 3% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > 5% → 触发\n• 中国石油专属：🟢 涨幅 > 2% | 🔴 跌幅 > 1%\n⚠️ 股价预警通知\n\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|\n| 601857 | 中国石油 | ¥11.95 | -7.51% | ¥-0.97 |\n| 601808 | 中海油服 | ¥17.90 | -6.82% | ¥-1.31 |"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6,"aggregated":"⚠️ 股价预警\n\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 | 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| 601857 | 中国石油 | ¥11.95 | -7.51% | ¥-0.97 | 2026-03-10 14:28:49 |\n| 601808 | 中海油服 | ¥17.90 | -6.82% | ¥-1.31 | 2026-03-10 14:28:49 |\n| 600256 | 广汇能源 | ¥6.71 | -5.36% | ¥-0.38 | 2026-03-10 14:28:49 |\n| 600583 | 海油工程 | ¥7.20 | -4.13% | ¥-0.31 | 2026-03-10 14:28:49 |\n| 000852 | 石化机械 | ¥8.08 | -3.92% | ¥-0.33 | 2026-03-10 14:28:49 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > 3% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > 5% → 触发\n• 中国石油专属：🟢 涨幅 > 2% | 🔴 跌幅 > 1%\n⚠️ 股价预警通知\n\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|\n| 601857 | 中国石油 | ¥11.95 | -7.51% | ¥-0.97 |\n| 601808 | 中海油服 | ¥17.90 | -6.82% | ¥-1.31 |","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773124581431}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a29e300","parentId":"5cf4617c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:37:01.828Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"由于 Tushare token 无效，我需要使用备用数据源（东方财富）来获取实时股价数据，然后按照预警规则进行过滤。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我看到有一些现有的数据文件。由于 Tushare token 无效，让我使用东方财富或同花顺的网页数据来获取实时股价。我将创建一个使用 web 抓取或 API 的脚本：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_50bcf9d08267495481cfb3f9","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n从东方财富获取实时股价数据\n使用东方财富 API: https://push2.eastmoney.com/api/qt/ulist/get\n\"\"\"\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport requests\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 读取自选股列表\nwatchlist_path = os.path.expanduser('~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/watchlist.txt')\nstocks = []\nstock_names = {}\n\ntry:\n    with open(watchlist_path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        for line in f:\n            line = line.strip()\n            if line and '|' in line:\n                code, name = line.split('|', 1)\n                # 转换代码格式为东方财富格式\n                # 60xxxx -> 1.60xxxx (上海)\n                # 00xxxx -> 0.00xxxx (深圳)\n                # 9866.HK -> 120.9866 (港股)\n                # AAPL -> 105.AAPL (美股)\n                if '.HK' in code:\n                    hk_code = code.replace('.HK', '')\n                    secid = f\"120.{hk_code}\"\n                elif '.' in code:\n                    secid = code  # 已有格式\n                elif code.startswith('6') or code.startswith('9') or code.startswith('5'):\n                    secid = f\"1.{code}\"  # 上海\n                elif code.startswith('8') or code.startswith('4'):\n                    secid = f\"1.{code}\"  # 北交所\n                else:\n                    secid = f\"0.{code}\"  # 深圳\n                \n                stocks.append(secid)\n                stock_names[secid] = name\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"读取自选股列表出错：{e}\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\nif not stocks:\n    print(\"自选股列表为空\")\n    sys.exit(1)\n\nprint(f\"自选股数量：{len(stocks)}\")\nprint(f\"股票列表：{stocks}\")\n\n# 东方财富实时行情 API\n# fields 说明：\n# f43=最新价，f44=涨跌额，f170=涨跌幅，f84=成交量，f85=成交额\n# f46=昨收，f47=今开，f48=最高，f49=最低\nfields = \"f43,f44,f170,f84,f85,f46,f47,f48,f49\"\nsecids = ','.join(stocks)\n\nurl = f\"https://push2.eastmoney.com/api/qt/ulist/get?fltt=2&invt=2&fields={fields}&secids={secids}\"\n\nprint(f\"请求 URL: {url}\")\n\ntry:\n    response = requests.get(url, timeout=10)\n    response.raise_for_status()\n    data = response.json()\n    \n    print(f\"API 返回：{json.dumps(data, ensure_ascii=False)[:500]}\")\n    \n    if data.get('data') and data['data'].get('diff'):\n        results = data['data']['diff']\n        \n        # 输出数据\n        output_lines = []\n        header = \"代码，名称，当前价，涨跌额，涨跌幅，昨收，今开，最高，最低，成交量，成交额，时间\"\n        output_lines.append(header)\n        \n        current_time = datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n        \n        for item in results:\n            code = item.get('f1', '')  # 代码\n            name = stock_names.get(f\"{item.get('f13','')}.{code}\", item.get('f2', ''))  # 名称\n            price = item.get('f43', 0)  # 当前价\n            change_amt = item.get('f44', 0)  # 涨跌额\n            change_pct = item.get('f170', 0)  # 涨跌幅\n            pre_close = item.get('f46', 0)  # 昨收\n            open_price = item.get('f47', 0)  # 今开\n            high = item.get('f48', 0)  # 最高\n            low = item.get('f49', 0)  # 最低\n            volume = item.get('f84', 0)  # 成交量\n            amount = item.get('f85', 0)  # 成交额\n            \n            # 格式化代码（去掉市场前缀）\n            if '.' in code:\n                code = code.split('.')[1]\n            \n            line = f\"{code},{name},{price:.2f},{change_amt:.2f},{change_pct:.2f},{pre_close:.2f},{open_price:.2f},{high:.2f},{low:.2f},{volume},{amount},{current_time}\"\n            output_lines.append(line)\n            print(line)\n        \n        # 保存到 realtime-data.txt\n        output_path = os.path.expanduser('~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt')\n        with open(output_path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            f.write('\\n'.join(output_lines))\n        \n        print(f\"\\n数据已保存到：{output_path}\")\n        print(f\"共 {len(results)} 条数据\")\n    else:\n        print(\"未获取到实时数据\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n        \nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"获取实时数据出错：{e}\")\n    import traceback\n    traceback.print_exc()\n    sys.exit(1)\n","path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get_realtime_data.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773124581433}}
